title: Sidewall, 1800–10
creditline: Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt
description: Horizontal rectangle. Vertical lozenge pattern of foliage, with floral inserts in each lozenge and floral rosettes at each angle of the lozenges. Printed in colors on mustard-yellow ground.
